            "title": "不甩美伊戰爭，國際AI大廠創新高！？台廠供應鏈最後上車時機！",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>上週末美伊停火談判破裂，中東地緣政治衝突未解，原油價格大漲並回歸到每桶 100 美元之上，但 VIX 指數卻下跌！VIX 指數自 3/27 創本波段新高後，就開始逐步降低，顯示雖然消息面還是導致股市與原物料價格波動，但實際上恐慌心態已經逐步減輕，資金會逐步回流風險性資產。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6418502/l/7e02ed1c6936e8bbd00c1d22e3a4e404.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">不甩美伊戰爭，國際AI大廠創新高！？台廠供應鏈最後上車時機！(圖:shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>VIX 指數回落期間，資金跑入那些個股？我們從 4 月份創今年或者歷史新高的國際股市來觀察</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>SUMCO(勝高)(3436-TYO)：全球第二大半導體矽晶圓製造商，漲逾 49%，創今年新高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>日東紡 (3110-TYO)：全球「高階玻纖布」領導廠。漲逾 175%，創今年新高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>應材 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMAT-US</a>)：全球最大的半導體製造設備和服務供應商，漲逾 48%，創歷史新高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Onto Innovation(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ONTO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ONTO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ONTO-US</a>)：先進製程瑕疵檢測、量測（計量）與軟體分析等，漲逾 55%，創歷史新高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>KLA(科磊)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:KLAC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/KLAC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">KLAC-US</a>)：晶圓檢測、光罩檢測、計量技術及資料分析軟體，漲逾 36%，創歷史新高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Lumentum(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LITE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LITE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LITE-US</a>)：光電元件供應商，矽光子與 CPO 兩大技術，漲逾 130%，創歷史新高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Coherent(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)：化合物半導體材料、光模組及工業雷射業務，漲逾 58%，創歷史新高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Monolithic Power Systems(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MPWR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MPWR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MPWR-US</a>)：雲端運算、電信、汽車、工業和消費性電子等電源管理，漲逾 44%，創歷史新高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>更多的投資策略與選股資訊都在－</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>LINE@ <a href=\"https://user225916.pse.is/money668\">https://user225916.pse.is/money668</a></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>頻道連結 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@money66868\">https://www.youtube.com/@money66868</a></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>上面國際大廠雖然產品差異大，但最大的共同點，卻還是受惠於 AI 基礎建設需求高成長，雖然輝達、博通與美光等個股未創歷史新高，但資金還是在 AI 產業鏈中輪動。台股大盤距離歷史新高僅一小小步，是本波資金回流的資金盛宴中，最受惠的市場之一，可以從國際股市觀察相關的產業鏈機會。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電 3 月營收高達 4151 億元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>，創單月歷史新高，4/16 的法說會還會再有好消息，台積電供應鏈一直是替投資朋友追蹤的標的，目前多檔創下歷史新高，還有哪些個股可留意？</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>AI ASIC 產業鏈績優股名單，給投資朋友參考－</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>矽晶圓：台勝科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3532:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3532\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3532-TW</a>)、環球晶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6488:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6488\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6488-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>玻纖布：富喬 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1815:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1815\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1815-TW</a>)、台玻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1802:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1802\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1802-TW</a>)、建榮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5340:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5340\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5340-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>半導體檢測：閎康 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3587:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3587\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3587-TW</a>)、汎銓 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6830:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6830\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6830-TW</a>)、宜特 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3289:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3289\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3289-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>測試介面：穎崴 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6515:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6515\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6515-TW</a>)、旺矽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6223:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6223\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6223-TW</a>)、精測 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6510:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6510\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6510-TW</a>)、雍智科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6683:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6683\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6683-TW</a>)、創新服務 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:7828:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-ev